LEARNnow — DAY-2 Progress (Hinglish)

Aaj ke kaam (practical + realistic):

1) SecurityConfig fix kiya (Postman friendly)
- HTTP Basic enable: /api/** ke liye auth required, baaki sab permitAll.
- CSRF disabled (dev/testing ke liye easy POST/PUT).
- Tip: application-dev.yml me fixed creds rakhna better hota hai (user/password) taaki console-wali random password dependency na rahe.

2) User flow cleanup (controller + service)
- UserController: @RestController + base path /api/users.
- Endpoints:
  - POST /api/users/add → user create
  - GET /api/users → list users
  - GET /api/users/{id} → single user (404 if not found)
- UserService: getUser() now uses findById + Optional (lazy proxy issue avoid), getUsers() uses findAll().

3) Repository bug fix
- UserRepo se galat custom method hata diya (User findAll(List<User> ...)).
- Ab sirf JpaRepository<User, Long> se sab CRUD ready.

4) pom.xml slim kiya (Postman testing ke liye minimal deps)
- Rakha: web, data-jpa, security, mysql-connector, devtools, lombok, test.
- Commented: actuator, web-services, validation, Swagger/OpenAPI, H2, security-test.
- Note: Actuator/Swagger ko later enable karenge jab endpoints stable ho jayenge.

5) Config
- application.yml: active profile dev.
- application-dev.yml: MySQL dev URL + creds set; JPA ddl-auto=update (abhi ke liye).

6) Postman testing
- Auth: Basic Auth (username=user, password=<dev password>).
- Paths sahi use karo:
  - POST http://localhost:8080/api/users/add
  - GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
  - GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/{id}
- Pehle /add hit kiya to 404 aaya (static resource add) — path incorrect tha. Ab /api/users/add use karo.

Known items (parked for kal)
- spring-boot:repackage se maven plugin error aaya; abhi spring-boot:run use karo; plugin fix kal address karenge.
- DTOs + jakarta validation + global exception handler.
- Flyway V1__init.sql (Topic/Video) + MySQL dev migrations.
- TopicController: POST/GET + Swagger (phir actuator health).

Short motivation
- Small wins daily. Ab POST/GET users clean ho gaye; kal se Topic + Flyway glue karte hain. Yeh flow interview-ready direction me ja raha hai.

